WEBVTT

00:00.040 --> 00:03.880
Does your wife ever get irritated at you for playing around with her,

00:03.881 --> 00:06.721
smacking her butt, or just harassing her all day?

00:06.722 --> 00:09.881
Well, research shows that couples who engage in playful

00:09.882 --> 00:13.561
teasing behavior and make fun of each other in a light hearted way

00:13.562 --> 00:17.401
are actually a lot more satisfied and happier in their relationship.

00:17.402 --> 00:18.561
Remind her of that. So yeah,

00:18.562 --> 00:20.535
she might get annoyed, but don't stop.
